page.title: 10MY TYPICAL SUNDAY
page.content: MY TYPICAL DAY IS GET UP AT 8 AM AND GET DRESSED,THEN I HAVE BREAKFAST.AFTER THAT I MAKE MY BED.WHEN I HAVE FINISHED DOING THAT I FINISH OFF MY HOMEWORK.NORMALLY THAT TAKES UNTIL LUNCHTIME. THEN I HAVE LUNCH, AND WASH UP. AFTER THAT MY FAMILY AND I GO UP TO MY GRAN'S AND WE TAKE THE DOG FOR A WALK. AT MY GRAN'S WE HAVE A DRINK AND A SLICE OF CAKE. OVER THE DOWNS WE WALK FOR TWO OR THREE MILES. WHEN WE GO HOME WE HAVE TEA OF A ROAST OR A SALAD. AFTERWARDS I HAVE A BATH AND WASH MY HAIR. THEN I WATCH TELEVISION OR READ. BEFORE I HAVE MY SUPPER I DO MY FORGOTTEN HOMEWORK.FOR MY SUPPER I HAVE A BAKED POTATO AND A CAN OF COKE. THEN I CLEAN MY TEETH, GO TO BED AND GO TO SLEEP.
